Magic Singles

", "text": "

Looking to buy or sell Magic the Gathering singles?

", "sub_text_one": "
Buying

1. Submit your list online using our digital storefront

2. We will gather the requested singles and call you when your order is ready for pickup

3. There is no limit to how many cards you can put on your list

Selling

1. Submit your buylist online using our digital storefront

2. Bring your cards into the store for a review

3. We will offer your choice of cash or store credit based on the value of the cards

4. There is no limit to how many cards you can submit on an online buylist

5. No more than 10 cards may be sold per customer per day on a walk-in bases

", "sub_text_two": "

We sell boosters and boxes of these TCGs!

", "logo_1": 29, "logo_2": 30, "logo_3": 31, "wagtail_admin_comments": []}

", "whats_new_text": "

Frosthaven is the story of a small outpost far to the north of the capital city of White Oak, an outpost barely surviving the harsh weather as well as invasions from forces both known and unknown.

There, a group of mercenaries at the end of their rope will help bring back this settlement from the edge of destruction. Not only will they have to deal with the harsh elements, but there are other, far more dangerous threats out in the unforgiving cold as well.

There are Algox, the bigger, more yeti-like cousins of the Inox, attacking from the mountains Lurkers flooding in from the northern sea and rumors of machines that wander the frozen wastes of their own free will.

The party of mercenaries must face all of these perils, and perhaps in doing so, make peace with these new races so they can work together against even more sinister forces.

\", \"description\": \"

Hello gamers and welcome to another board game spotlight! Today we'll be looking at the cuddliest cat pushing game around, Boop!

In Boop, two players place kittens on the bed, pushing them around in order to get 3 in a row, turning them into cats! Place 3 cats in a row and you win!

Each player starts the game with 8 kittens and a pool of 8 cats to upgrade them. Players take turns placing one kitten on the bed at a time. When placed, a kitten pushes (or "boops") each other piece around it one space away. Booped pieces don't boop other pieces, so carefully placed pieces can keep kittens in place! If a piece is booped off the bed it returns to that player's pool.

If a player manages to get 3 of their kittens in a row in any direction, they are removed from the board and three cats are placed in that player's pool. These cats replace the kittens, so a player only has 8 pieces to place at a time. These cats can then be placed like kittens, except that they can't be booped by kittens! If you get 3 cats in a row, you win!

If you're looking for a fast, adorable and light-hearted game that still has a fair amount of strategy, Boop is for you!

content.text: Looking to buy or sell Magic the Gathering singles?
content.title: Magic Singles
content.sub_text:
How it works:
Buying
  1. Submit your list online using our digital storefront
  2. We will gather the requested singles and call you when your order is ready for pickup
  3. There is no limit to how many cards you can put on your list
Selling
  1. Submit your buylist online using our digital storefront
    Bring your cards into the store for a review
  2. We will offer your choice of cash or store credit based on the value of the cards
  3. There is no limit to how many cards you can submit on an online buylist
  4. No more than 10 cards may be sold per customer per day on a walk-in bases

content.name: Flesh and Blood TCG Classic Constructed Charity To
content.title: Flesh and Blood TCG Classic Constructed Charity Tournament Pre-Registration (Dec. 18th)
content.description:
Join us for our first Classic Constructed Flesh and Blood Tournament on Sunday December 18th!



Format: Classic Constructed https://fabtcg.com/resources/gameplay-formats/classic-constructed/



Time: Starts promptly at 1PM after our Learn to Play session.



Entry: $10. Limited to 16 players.



Prizes: We are giving out a full Armory Kit for this event, so everyone regardless of final standings will walk away with some cool promos! Additionally, there will be store credit prizes based on attendance paid out to winning records.

content.about_text:
Black Moon Games earns its namesake from my former group of fantasy Dungeons and Dragons mercenaries... The Black Moon Mercenary Guild!

  • Now a prominent fixture of the community in New Hampshires Upper Valley, we offer the widest selection of board games, tabletop games, trading cards, and puzzles in the area.
  • You can find us directly underneath the Lebanon Village Market, next to Sunrise Buffet and the Laundry Spa. Just head towards the Lebanon village square and turn into one of the parking lots by the Market and head down the stairs.
  • We hope to see you soon!
  • -- Tony Vandenberg, Owner

content.title: MTG Chaos Sealed Deck Promopalooza
content.description:
Join us for a very special Sealed Deck tournament and walk away with a ton of promos!

Format: CHAOS Sealed Deck (Each player will select 6 Standard Draft Booster Packs of their choice when they arrive)

Time: Deckbuilding starts promptly at 12PM on Saturday December 24th. Show up earlier to register.

Entry: $35. Limited to 16 players. Pre-register to secure your spot!

Prizes: EVERY player in this event will walk away with a bunch of older Magic promos. FNM promos? Buy a Box promos? Game Day promos? Promo packs? YES! In addition to the promopalooza, each player will win 1 Standard Draft Booster Pack per match win after 3 rounds of play.

content.text: Looking to buy or sell Magic the Gathering singles?
content.title: TCGS
content.sub_text_one:
Buying

1. Submit your list online using our digital storefront

2. We will gather the requested singles and call you when your order is ready for pickup

3. There is no limit to how many cards you can put on your list

Selling

1. Submit your buylist online using our digital storefront

2. Bring your cards into the store for a review

3. We will offer your choice of cash or store credit based on the value of the cards

4. There is no limit to how many cards you can submit on an online buylist

5. No more than 10 cards may be sold per customer per day on a walk-in bases

Add whatever else you want to this section.
content.sub_text_two: We sell boosters and boxes of these TCGs!

content.whats_new_text:
Frosthaven is the story of a small outpost far to the north of the capital city of White Oak, an outpost barely surviving the harsh weather as well as invasions from forces both known and unknown.

There, a group of mercenaries at the end of their rope will help bring back this settlement from the edge of destruction. Not only will they have to deal with the harsh elements, but there are other, far more dangerous threats out in the unforgiving cold as well.

There are Algox, the bigger, more yeti-like cousins of the Inox, attacking from the mountains Lurkers flooding in from the northern sea and rumors of machines that wander the frozen wastes of their own free will.

The party of mercenaries must face all of these perils, and perhaps in doing so, make peace with these new races so they can work together against even more sinister forces.

Frosthaven is a standalone adventure from the designer and publisher of Gloomhaven that features sixteen new characters, three new races, more than twenty new enemies, more than one hundred new items, and a new, 100-scenario campaign.

[{"type": "product", "value": {"name": "

Boop!

", "description": "

Hello gamers and welcome to another board game spotlight! Today we'll be looking at the cuddliest cat pushing game around, Boop!

In Boop, two players place kittens on the bed, pushing them around in order to get 3 in a row, turning them into cats! Place 3 cats in a row and you win!

Each player starts the game with 8 kittens and a pool of 8 cats to upgrade them. Players take turns placing one kitten on the bed at a time. content.text: Looking to buy or sell Magic the Gathering singles?
content.title: TCGS
content.sub_text_one:
Buying

1. Submit your list online using our digital storefront

2. We will gather the requested singles and call you when your order is ready for pickup

3. There is no limit to how many cards you can put on your list

Selling

1. Submit your buylist online using our digital storefront

2. Bring your cards into the store for a review

3. We will offer your choice of cash or store credit based on the value of the cards

4. There is no limit to how many cards you can submit on an online buylist

5. No more than 10 cards may be sold per customer per day on a walk-in bases
content.sub_text_two: We sell boosters and boxes of these TCGs!

content.about_text:
Black Moon Games earns its namesake from my former group of fantasy Dungeons and Dragons mercenaries... The Black Moon Mercenary Guild!

Now a prominent fixture of the community in New Hampshires Upper Valley, we offer the widest selection of board games, tabletop games, trading cards, and puzzles in the area.

You can find us directly underneath the Lebanon Village Market, next to Sunrise Buffet and the Laundry Spa. Just head towards the Lebanon village square and turn into one of the parking lots by the Market and head down the stairs.

We hope to see you soon!

-- Tony Vandenberg, Owner

fields.about_text:
Black Moon Games earns its namesake from my former group of fantasy Dungeons and Dragons mercenaries... The Black Moon Mercenary Guild!

Now a prominent fixture of the community in New Hampshires Upper Valley, we offer the widest selection of board games, tabletop games, trading cards, and puzzles in the area.

You can find us in our new location in the Northfield Plaza next to Panera Bread and Verizon, bigger and better than ever!

We hope to see you soon!

-- Tony Vandenberg, Owner

fields.name: Friday Night Magic
fields.description:
Join us every Friday for varying Magic formats for fun and prizes!

Drafts award booster packs for each match win!

Constructed awards store credit to winning records after 3 rounds!

Players earn special promo packs every week!

--->You can not use store credit or gift cards to pay for game space events<---

fields.name: Flesh and Blood TCG Classic Constructed Charity To
fields.description:
Join us for our first Classic Constructed Flesh and Blood Tournament on Sunday December 18th!



Format: Classic Constructed https://fabtcg.com/resources/gameplay-formats/classic-constructed/



Time: Starts promptly at 1PM after our Learn to Play session.



Entry: $10. Limited to 16 players.



Prizes: We are giving out a full Armory Kit for this event, so everyone regardless of final standings will walk away with some cool promos! Additionally, there will be store credit prizes based on attendance paid out to winning records.

fields.name: MTG Chaos Sealed Deck Promopalooza
fields.description:
Join us for a very special Sealed Deck tournament and walk away with a ton of promos!
  • Format: CHAOS Sealed Deck (Each player will select 6 Standard Draft Booster Packs of their choice when they arrive)

  • Time: Deckbuilding starts promptly at 12PM on Saturday December 24th. Show up earlier to register. Entry: $35. Limited to 16 players. Pre-register to secure your spot!

  • Prizes: EVERY player in this event will walk away with a bunch of older Magic promos. FNM promos? Buy a Box promos? Game Day promos? Promo packs? YES! In addition to the promopalooza, each player will win 1 Standard Draft Booster Pack per match win after 3 rounds of play.

fields.name: Open Play
fields.description:
Join us in the gamespace for Open Play and play any game you'd like! Open Play is available from open to close as long as scheduled events aren't running. You have access to our full board game library as part of your reservation!

Entry is $5, and you receive $5 in store credit when you register.

fields.name: Pokemon TCG League
fields.description:
Join us every Tuesday for casual Pokemon TCG Open Play. Bring your favorite deck, or learn to play from our veteran Trainers and Professor! Each player will earn a promo for attending!

Runs from 3PM to 6PM, drop by anytime!

Entry is $5 per person, and each attendee gets a booster pack of their choice!

fields.description:

fields.name: Lunar Lounge Reservations
fields.description:
Book our private game room the Lunar Lounge for up to 6 people for four hours and enjoy a nice big table, over 100 hand-painted D&D miniatures and Warlock Tiles to use, access to our board game library of over 200 titles, and a smart TV to cast to!

Reservation is $50 for a group of up to 6 people, and you receive $50 in store credit back.

-Reservations cannot be paid with store credit or gift cards-

fields.name: Phyrexia All Will Be One Prerelease Weekend
fields.description:
Join us for four Prerelease events where you can play with the new Magic set a week before release! This will be our last event in downtown Lebanon, as we officially open our new location the following week!

Each event is Sealed Deck using Prerelease Packs (6 Draft Booster Packs and a foil promo rare or mythic). Each player will win one Set Booster Pack per match win after 3 rounds of play.

Deckbuilding starts promptly at the listed time. Show up earlier to register. You must have a Wizards Account to play.

Friday Feb. 3rd: 6PM-10PM
Saturday Feb. 4th: 11AM-3PM
Saturday Feb. 4th: 4PM-8PM
Sunday Feb. 5th: 1PM-5PM

Each event is capped at 24 players. Pre-register to secure your spot! Gift cards/Store Credit cannot be used for event entry.

fields.text: Looking to buy or sell Magic the Gathering singles?
fields.sub_text_one:
Buying

1. Submit your list online using our digital storefront

2. We will gather the requested singles and call you when your order is ready for pickup

3. There is no limit to how many cards you can put on your list

Selling

1. Submit your buylist online using our digital storefront

2. Bring your cards into the store for a review

3. We will offer your choice of cash or store credit based on the value of the cards

4. There is no limit to how many cards you can submit on an online buylist

5. No more than 10 cards may be sold per customer per day on a walk-in bases

fields.whats_new_text:
After nearly 9 years in downtown Lebanon, NH we are upgrading and expanding the store in our new location at 267 Plainfield Rd in West Lebanon. The new store will be bigger and better, and we can't wait to unveil it at our Grand Opening on Friday February 10th!

Our last day of business in downtown Lebanon will be Sunday, February 5th. We will be closed starting on Monday the 6th in order to pack up and move the store to our new location, and reopen on Friday February 10th.

2023 is shaping up to be an awesome year for Black Moon Games, and we can't wait to see all of you at our new and improved West Lebanon location!
